original_title: A Day of Intrigue with Sybil & Alyssa
overview: Playing the judge between your beautiful girlfriend, Sybil, and her hated, still very sexy cousin, Alyssia wont be an easy ride. They both want the house they inherited from their aunt for themselves and you should help them to get into an agreement. But as you dig deeper into their intrigues, you realize that not everything is as it seems. What if you were wrong about Alyssia and Sybil is the culprit? Only you can find out the truth!
title: A Day of Intrigue with Sybil & Alyssa
